question: For final semester students, you need to do the following matters:
answer: 1. Please ensure your Professional Skills Certificate (PSC) is completed. It is one of the requirement to graduate. 2. Please ensure your details in the MyUTM, especially your personal telephone number and e-mail are updated and latest. Your Senate letter will be emailed to you. 3. Please fill up the google form provided for the Academic Office of Faculty of Mechanical Engineering. The Academic Office want to have a list of students will be graduating this semester. Link: https://forms.gle/f4NYSGSrwEm93MwMA
